ear regression" class=3D"wp-image-196051"></figure></div>


<ul class=3D"wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Total Sum of Squares (TSS)</strong> is defined as the sum of er=
rors of the data points from the mean of the response variable. Mathematica=
lly TSS is,</li>
</ul>


<div class=3D"wp-block-image">
<figure class=3D"aligncenter"><img loading=3D"lazy" decoding=3D"async" widt=
