#R-squared value
<span class=3D"hljs-built_in">print</span>( <span class=3D"hljs-string">"R-=
squared: "</span>,<span class=3D"hljs-built_in">r2_score</span>( y_test, y_=
pred ) )</code><button class=3D"copy-button btn btn-dark rounded-3 fs-12">C=
opy Code</button></pre>



