<pre class=3D"wp-block-code"><code data-highlighted=3D"yes" class=3D"hljs l=
anguage-scss"><span class=3D"hljs-built_in">print</span>(X_train_lm.shape)
<span class=3D"hljs-built_in">print</span>(X_train_lm.shape)</code><button =
class=3D"copy-button btn btn-dark rounded-3 fs-12">Copy Code</button></pre>



