n" data-bs-toggle=3D"collapse" data-bs-target=3D"#faq-question-171654516134=
1" aria-expanded=3D"false" aria-controls=3D"faq-question-1716545161341">Q4.=
 What is a basic example of linear regression?</button></h2><div id=3D"faq-=
question-1716545161341" class=3D"accordion-collapse collapse " data-bs-pare=
nt=3D"#accordionFaq"><div class=3D"accordion-body border-0"><p class=3D"fw-=
light text-dark-tertiary schema-faq-answer">A. A basic linear regression ex=
ample involves predicting a person=E2=80=99s weight based on height. In thi=
s scenario, height is the independent variable, while weight is the depende=
nt variable. The relationship between height and weight is modeled using a =
simple linear equation, where the weight is estimated as a function of the =
height.</p></div></div></div><div class=3D"accordion-item mb-4 border-0 rou=
nded-3 schema-faq-section"><h2 class=3D"accordion-header rounded-3 border-0=
 schema-faq-question"><button class=3D"accordion-button collapsed shadow-0 =
